The text says: *"C++20 brings us modules... and one I'm looking forward to actually being implemented fairly soon."*

*   **The Clue:** C++20 modules were standardized in 2020, but widespread, stable implementation (especially in MSVC and Clang) was still maturing and facing adoption hurdles in **2022 and 2023**.
